action.description: Taken from Secretary's desk. Placed on General File.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 807.)Reprinting dispensed with.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved, as amended. (Yeas: 20, Nays: None, Excused: 1.) To printer.From printer. To re-engrossment. Re-engrossed. Second reprint. To Assembly.In Assembly.
